Dhaqaalaha caalamiga ah ayaa hoos u dhacay Shiinaha: sida lagu sheegay warbaahinta 16ka Maarso, dhaqaalaha Shiinaha ayaa si weyn u dhacay labadii bilood ee ugu horreysay ee sanadka 2020 sababo la xiriira tallaabooyinka ay dowladu qaadatay si loo xakameeyo faafitaanka fayraska, iibka tafaariiqda ayaa hoos u dhacay 20.5%.
