Marka ay qalalaan, warqad lagu duubay ayaa loo isticmaalaa in la damiyo biyaha (iyo in laga furo albaabka marka loo baahdo).
Tallaabadan ayaa ka hortagta in gacmaha lagu celiyo dhulka.
Ujeedada dhaqashada gacmaha ee nidaamka daryeelka caafimaadka waa in la tirtiro mikroorganismada cudurka qaba ("dhibka") iyo in laga fogaado gudbinta.
The New England Journal of Medicine waxay soo sheegtay in la'aanta gacmaha ay weli tahay mid aan la aqbali karin inta badan deegaanada caafimaadka, iyadoo dhakhaatiir iyo kalkaalisada tiro badan ay sii dayaan inay illoobaan inay gacmaha ku dhaqmaan ka hor inta aysan taaban bukaanka, taas oo keentay in ay faafiyaan mikroorganismada.
Daraasad ayaa muujisay in gacmaha la maydho iyo hababka kale ee fudud ay yareyn karaan heerarka cudurrada dhiigga ee ku saabsan qanjirka gacmaha ilaa 66 boqolkiiba. Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa daabacay warqad muujineysa heerarka gacmaha lagu maydho iyo gacmaha lagu maydho ee qaybta daryeelka caafimaadka.
Tilmaamaha fikradaha nadaafadda gacmaha ee WHO ayaa sidoo kale laga arki karaa boggeeda internetka si aad u hesho faallooyin dadweyne.
