Hase yeeshee, Machadka Virology ee Wuhan, inkastoo ay ku talineyso qiyaasta maalinlaha ah ee hal gram, waxay xustay in qiyaasta laba jeer ay aad u khatar badan tahay oo ay u dhintaan.
Bishii Maarso 28, 2020, FDA waxay oggolaatay isticmaalka degdegga ah ee hydroxychloroquine iyo chlorokuine iyadoo la raacayo siyaasadda dhakhaatiirta daryeela COVID-19 bukaanka. Tilmaamaha Shiinaha ee daabacaadda 7aad ayaa sidoo kale ku jira interferon, ribavirin, ama umifenovir si loo isticmaalo COVID-19.
Xogta hore waxay muujineysaa in qiyaaso sare oo ribavirin ah loo baahan yahay si loo xakameeyo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitazoksanide waxaa lagu talinayaa in lagu sameeyo daraasado in vivo oo dheeri ah kadib markii la muujiyey in la joojiyo SARS-CoV-2 heerar hoose. Daraasaduhu waxay muujinayaan in priming-ka bilowga ah ee borotiinka bararka ee serine transmembrane protease 2 (TMPRSS2) uu muhiim u yahay gelitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyada oo loo marayo isdhexgalka soo dhaweynta ACE2.
Daraasadaha ku saabsan chlorokuin iyo hydroxychloroquine oo leh ama aan lahayn azithromycin waxay leeyihiin xaddidaad weyn oo ka hortagtay bulshada caafimaadka inay isticmaalaan daaweynta iyada oo aan la helin cilmi baaris dheeraad ah. Oseltamivir ma xakameeyo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro mana laha door loo yaqaan daaweynta COVID-19.
Dhibaatooyinka duufaanta cytokine waxay ku dhici karaan COVID-19 heerar culus oo horumarsan.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in hydroxychloroquine ay u badan tahay inay leedahay astaamo antisitokin ah. Tocilizumab waxaa lagu daray tilmaamaha daaweynta ee Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha ka dib markii la dhammeystiray daraasad yar.
Daawada ayaa hadda la socdaa tijaabooyin heer qaran oo heer qaran ah oo heer qaran ah oo ku yaal Talyaaniga kadib markii ay ku soo bandhigtay natiijooyin wanaagsan dadka qaba cudur daran.
Waxaa lagu daraa baaritaano dhiig oo feritine ah oo lagu ogaado duufaanta sitokin, waxaana loo maleynayaa in daawadaasi ay ka hortagto duufaanta sitokin, taas oo ah sababta keenta dhimashada dadka qaar ee saameeyay.
Sanadkii 2017, antagonistada interleukin-6 ee FDA ayaa lagu ansixiyay iyadoo la raacayo daraasadaha kiisaska dib u eegista ee daaweynta cudurka sii deynta sitokin ee steroid-ka ee loo yaqaan 'refractor cytokine syndrome' oo loo yaqaan 'car T cell therapy'.
Ilaa hadda, ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo la xakameyn karo oo muujinaya in tocilizumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo CRS ah.
Wareejinta antibodies-ka la nadiifiyey iyo kuwa la isku xidhay ee ay soo saaraan nidaamka dadka ka bogsaday COVID-19 dadka u baahan ayaa la baranayo sida habka tallaalka aan la tallaalin.
istiraatiijiyadan ayaa lagu tijaabiyey SARS natiijooyin aan la xaqiijin.
Neutralization virus waa habka shaqada ee lagu filayo in daaweynta antibody-ka aan la shaqeyn karin ay dhexdhexaad ka noqon karto difaaca ka dhanka ah SARS-CoV-2.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, habab kale, sida cytotoxicity-ka unugyada ku tiirsan antibodies iyo/ama fagositosis, ayaa sidoo kale suuragal ah.
Nooc kale oo daaweynta antibody-yada xasaasiga ah, tusaale ahaan, oo isticmaalaya antibodies monoclonal oo la soo saaray, ayaa la horumarinayaa.
Wax soo saarka serum-ka soo kabashada, oo ah qayb ka mid ah dareeraha dhiigga bukaanka oo soo kabsaday oo ku jira unugyo gaar ah oo ka dhan ah fayraska, ayaa la kordhin karaa si loo isticmaalo si dhakhso leh.
